('101562', '6503077991', 5, 't', 1, 6, 0, 6, '2021-04-13', 'I used to use the Murad SPF 30 Day Cream in the orange tube.  Then I tried this one, being in my 60s and needing better hydration.  I really like it.  I was afraid it might be too much moisture and cause breakouts, but it was perfect.  I love that it has SPF 30, too; I don‚Äôt even open my window blinds till I have sunscreen on.  I‚Äôve noticed that my little creases and wrinkles look better since I‚Äôve been using this.  It doesn‚Äôt have a fragrance, per se; no perfume added.  But I love the way it smells; it smells very fresh.  The scent goes away as soon as it dries.  I highly recommend it.', 'Awesome moisturizer for mature skin', 'fair', 'blue', 'combination', 'blonde', 'P4039', 'Perfecting Day Cream Broad Spectrum SPF 30 PA+++', 'Murad', 65),
