('112418', '1422188188', 5, 't', 0.6666669845581055, 3, 1, 2, '2023-03-14', 'I have tried a few similar moisturizers in the barrier supporting category, including skinfix and the Dr Jart ceramidin, and I find this one to be the best for my skin. The texture is so interesting - kind of like a thick gel-cream, and it gives a ton of hydration without sitting heavy or greasy on the skin. My skin is combination but I do use adapalene so when I need some extra hydration I‚Äôll layer an occlusive over this at night and that works well for me. I can wear it both at night and during the day under makeup. Love the smell and I love the feel of the glass jar over plastic (better for the environment too!).', 'Love!', 'fair', 'brown', 'oily', NULL, 'P479339', 'Strength Trainer Peptide Boost Moisturizer', 'OLEHENRIKSEN', 51),
