('112455', '2238245706', 5, 't', 1, 14, 0, 14, '2021-06-16', 'Within a week of using this 1-2x per day, I noticed a huge difference in my skin. You still need to pair with a moisturizing and hydrating serum/moisturizer, but my skin LOVES this product. KS always makes the best stuff.', 'LOVE this serum!', 'light', 'brown', 'combination', 'brown', 'P442867', 'Kx Active Concentrates Bio-Mimicking Peptides Serum', 'Kate Somerville', 98),
