('43461', '5319123605', 5, 't', 0.6666669845581055, 3, 1, 2, '2023-02-05', 'I switched to Clean ingredients years ago and so happy to see more companies emerge with safer options; in this case wild crafted ingredients from Jackson Hole Wy.  Effective serum & packaged in a glass bottle', 'Wild Crafted Ingredients', 'lightMedium', 'green', 'normal', 'blonde', 'P472302', 'Wild Nettle & Niacinamide Instant Firming Serum', 'alpyn beauty', 58),
('43462', '9562938819', 5, 't', 1, 7, 0, 7, '2023-02-03', 'I hate when products leave my face feeling sticky and especially hate when they pill.  This serum is unique in that it dries very quickly, not feeling tight and having a lack of moisture, but a sort of firming feeling that isn‚Äôt tingly or uncomfortable in any way.  It helps a lot with puffiness since it firms the skin so quickly.  Makeup and other skincare products can be applied soon afterward due to how fast this sets on the face, just be sure to spread it evenly all over and apply to the neck as well!  I find that this helps brighten and even tone as well, doesn‚Äôt necessarily help with blemishes but I believe this is good for dull skin, aging skin, and puffy skin.  I have inflammation in my body quite often and it will show on my face very clearly and this helps minimize that.  I like to press it in with my palms for better absorption as well.  I have yet to find a serum that works instantly like this one does.  Similar to their Melt Moisturizer, this does not interact badly with my other skincare products and makeup and primes my skin well for makeup application, unlike many other products that I own. that are finicky when it comes to layering well with other skincare items from other companies.  Like I said, I really hate pilling and just start rubbing my face when that happens (I have OCD).  Applying this serum is a very nice, cooling experience, and it does not smell like anything, just a bit herbal!', 'Surprisingly, firms instantly and dries quickly', 'light', 'hazel', 'combination', 'auburn', 'P472302', 'Wild Nettle & Niacinamide Instant Firming Serum', 'alpyn beauty', 58),
