('48716', '24461753113', 5, 't', 1, 2, 0, 2, '2023-03-15', 'I honestly never write reviews but i had to. I‚Äôve had oily skin since highschool. I‚Äôm 24 now, and it‚Äôs still a daily issue. I have to blot my face every 2 hours. I have tried SO many products. This product is the only one that actually stops the oil production. I am completely matte all day long. It‚Äôs actually insane. I just bought this product 2 days ago and will 100% be buying again. If you have oily skin, you seriously need this. I can‚Äôt believe I found this product on a whim just shopping around the store. 10/10', 'Matte All Day Long', 'lightMedium', 'brown', 'oily', 'brown', 'P504810', 'Priming Moisturizer Balance Oil-Control Gel-Cream', 'Glossier', 25),
