('67115', '1021959876', 3, 'f', 0.9230769872665404, 13, 1, 12, '2022-06-07', 'I love Emerald so thought I‚Äôd give Orchid and Phoenix a try and found them both to be just okay.  There are SO many great facial oils on the market; if this one sounds like it‚Äôs up your alley, give it a try.  I have incredibly dry and sensitive skin, and while this didn‚Äôt make me react at all, I didn‚Äôt feel like it brought anything to the table for me either.  I much prefer Herbivore Emerald, YTTP Superberry Dream Oil, Dermalogica Phyto Replenish Oil or BioElements Dewluxe.', 'It''s just okay', 'fairLight', 'green', 'dry', 'blonde', 'P400205', 'Orchid Antioxidant Beauty Face Oil - For Combination Skin', 'Herbivore', 74),
