('68564', '1272760256', 5, 't', 0.9285709857940674, 14, 1, 13, '2021-08-29', 'Wonderful! Keeps my skin clear and supple. It‚Äôs funny that the bad reviews are for the smell and not the performance of the product. I find the smell very natural, but I like essential oils. I do not like ‚Äúfake‚Äù floral scents or added fragrances, so this is alright by me.', 'Great Performance Product & Natural Scent', 'fair', 'brown', 'combination', 'brown', 'P379711', 'Rejuvenating Anti-Aging Serum', 'Tata Harper', 146),
('68565', '10332664876', 5, 't', 0.857142984867096, 7, 1, 6, '2021-07-19', 'Gorgeous skin care line. I only recently started using the Tata harper brand of products. Their moisturizer is amazing as well. So is this anti-aging serum. I feel like I am giving my skin a special treatment at the end of the day. The smell actually reminds me of Jasmine and rose flowers in my garden back in India. It smells so natural. I am not sure why few others are finding the smell so offensive. Perhaps the product is old? I am keeping my serum in the fridge hoping it would stay fresh longer. I do use it a couple times a week in the night as I want to save it for special occasions - when I‚Äôm feeling tired or need some pampering. I have used many serums from several other luxe brands including drunk elephant, Sunday Riley, Dr Strum, etc. I can honestly say this tops all of those brands, especially the serum.', 'Absolutely fantastic', 'mediumTan', 'brown', 'combination', 'black', 'P379711', 'Rejuvenating Anti-Aging Serum', 'Tata Harper', 146),
