('68801', '7688614823', 3, 't', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2022-11-11', 'i just finished this moisturizer, and here are my thoughts. it‚Äôs a fine moisturizer - not great, not terrible. i wouldn‚Äôt purchase again though. it has a very lightweight consistency. this would be a perfect moisturizer honestly for anyone with oily skin - however, as someone with dry skin, i have found that it is not hydrating enough at all for me. my skin typically prefers a thicker, more moisturizing cream to really hydrate my skin and this just did not do it for me. especially since i choose to wear mineral SPF, whenever i apply this in the morning under my SPF i find it leaves my skin extra dry. i think people with oily skin would really enjoy this moisturizer, but for me, it‚Äôs a pass. love the brand concept but formulations feel a little rushed. i do enjoy that the formula is non-comedogenic and it doesn‚Äôt have a strong fragrance.', 'not for dry skin - good if you have oily skin', 'fair', 'hazel', 'combination', NULL, 'P500094', 'Hydrating Oil-Free Gel Moisturizer', 'Community Sixty-Six', 25),
('68802', '1845711259', 4, 't', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2022-09-22', 'The idea of creating healthy habits takes 66 days hence, ‚ÄúCommunity sixty six‚Äú really made me love the brand off the bat; the packaging is informative with a guided amount usage tool too! However, that‚Äôs the only positive feedback I have, as all the product formulations are very poor. I feel like they spent a lot of time coming up with a great mission but didn‚Äôt spend that same time and/or attention on the formulas themselves. With that said, this was the BEST product out of ALL of the Community Sixty Six line. As someone with oily/acne-prone skin this is a good option as it doesn‚Äôt contain any fatty acids, alcohols, and/or esters! Clinique Moisture Surge 100hr Auto Replenishing Hydrator is still my go to though (at the same price point)', 'Community sixty sixes SUPERSTAR', 'lightMedium', 'brown', 'oily', 'brown', 'P500094', 'Hydrating Oil-Free Gel Moisturizer', 'Community Sixty-Six', 25),
('68803', '10315123751', 5, 't', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2022-09-22', 'I‚Äôm obsessed with this stuff. I have dry skin and this moisturizer is thick and hydrates is so well. Not oily at all, and no smell.', '', 'fair', NULL, 'combination', NULL, 'P500094', 'Hydrating Oil-Free Gel Moisturizer', 'Community Sixty-Six', 25),
('68804', '5883969217', 4, 't', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2022-09-22', 'It is a nice moisturizer that I enjoy using in the mornings. It is moisturizing enough for the summer weather and doesn‚Äôt make my makeup pill. I enjoy that it is fragrance-free and oil-free since I do have sensitive, combination skin.', '', 'lightMedium', 'brown', 'combination', 'brown', 'P500094', 'Hydrating Oil-Free Gel Moisturizer', 'Community Sixty-Six', 25),
