('79272', '1305330726', 5, 't', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2023-03-17', 'I always have a hard time finding a good moisturizer in the wintertime. I have oily, sensitive, acne-prone skin so lighter moisturizers are usually better for me in the summertime, but sometimes my skin gets dehydrated in the wintertime and the gel moisturizers just don‚Äôt cut it. The problem is that heavier creams tend to break me out, but I NEED hydration after retinol... so what to do???ENTER: this moisturizer. My skin stopped feeling dry after using it just once. I use it in the AM and sometimes PM on non-retinol nights. So glad I finally found a winter moisturizer that doesn‚Äôt break me out.', 'Great for dehydrated oily skin', 'tan', 'hazel', 'oily', NULL, 'P503690', 'Water Drench Hyaluronic Cloud Rich Barrier Moisturizer', 'Peter Thomas Roth', 58),
