('79274', '5051683809', 2, 'f', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2023-03-12', 'Honestly I wasn‚Äôt a fan of the consistency of this moisturizer, but it does feel nice if you plan on doing gua sha. However, it did break me out regardless of being non-comedogenic and I read other reviews of it breaking people out. It was pretty hydrating.', 'Not for me.', NULL, 'brown', 'combination', NULL, 'P503690', 'Water Drench Hyaluronic Cloud Rich Barrier Moisturizer', 'Peter Thomas Roth', 58),
