('9011', '41869864267', 5, 't', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2023-01-16', 'if you are looking for an honest review.. look no further!!!-I‚Äôve always been a huge cleanser person. I tend to not buy skincare that is too harsh so i stick with my masks, cleansers and moisturizers and I‚Äôve always known about the brand La Mer. Unfortunately, I am too broke to actually buy something full size but when I recently got some money out of sheer blindness I bought the mini for this cleansing foam just to try it out and I will say with much confidence, that you will not regret it. The smell is so so so amazing so if you are really into fragrance you will love this! I smells and feels so luxurious like you are being pampered at a spa :) A little goes a long way but from how often I use this because of how good it is, I might invest for the bigger size. If you have oily/combo skin this is a must!!! A little pricey but well worth it. Overall excellent, you get what you pay for and it did its job and did it well!!! Would recommend <333', 'love love love (not necessary) .. still love', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P416344', 'The Cleansing Foam', 'La Mer', 95),
('9012', '28637416731', 1, 'f', 0.6666669845581055, 3, 1, 2, '2022-12-01', 'As I get older, I wanted to pay more attention to my skin. About a year ago, I bought three La mer products.  Cleanser, treatment lotion and moisturizing cream. I read so many raving reviews and I really wanted to love them. But I couldn‚Äôt .  They are ok but I can find similar products which are 1/10 of the price. I had to constantly remind myself how much I paid to motivate myself to use the products before they expire..after a year of trying, I just gave up on them.. if you can, try to get the samples before committing to full sizes.', 'This isn‚Äôt for me', 'fair', 'brown', 'normal', 'black', 'P416344', 'The Cleansing Foam', 'La Mer', 95),
